content:
Digital Lending supports the end-to-end lending lifecycle across all retail loan products and channels in a unified lending platform. Create a loan application process that suits the needs of your clients, both self-serve and agent-assisted.

Your clients can apply for a loan during a time thatâ€™s convenient for them by using Digital Lending self-serve experience. An easy-to-configure Experience Cloud template supports the self-serve channel loan application experience to meet the needs of your clients.

To determine the categories and products that an applicant sees based on their Account context, and determine applicant loan eligibility, create product qualification rules. To show categories, products, and product attributes in Experience Cloud, use quote and order capture.

The Digital Lending agent-assisted application experience provides your bankers with a seamless loan application process. Show a banker the loan products that the applicant is eligible for by creating loan products, catalogs, attributes, classifications, and rules by using Product Catalog Management.

Give underwriters easy access to loan application details to make informed decisions by using Workbench. The underwriters can get a consolidated view of a submitted loan application on the application form product record page.

To configure settings, features, components, and a data model to create an end-to-end example of Digital Lending implementation, complete the steps documented in Set Up and Manage Digital Lending.

Set Up Digital Lending requires:

* Setting up Application Form Seller Item and Party Financial Asset objects for secured loans
* Creating product qualification rules
* Using Business Rules Engine decision matrix to ensure that a client uploads the required supporting documents when applying for a loan
* Salesforce Pricing for customized price adjustment methods
* Customizing Experience Cloud Pages for branded digital experiences
* Setting up Secure Self-Service Loan Assets for loan applications
* Creating Application Action Items for loan application processes
* Providing Agent Assisted Loan Applications for bankers to assist clients with loan applications
* Giving Underwriters easy access to loan application details through the Underwriter Console
title: Digital Lending Setup for Financial Services Cloud
